{"ts":"2026-07-19T03:43:33.684Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"append","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GH-601. dist/sdk/runtime.d.ts: PmActionOptions = Record<string, unknown> for mutation inputs; projected list rows equally untyped — field typos/wrong value types compile clean under strict and fail at runtime; listed-item id access not type-safe. Fix direction: derive per-action input types from the existing flag/schema contracts (single source, no hand-written duplicates) + typed projection rows; add type-level tests. Serves SDK-first (pm-usfg) consumer contract quality."},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-19T03:43:33.684Z"}],"before_hash":"1fce8ed212be7b97b10d097179cd697a324fd8c6a0068155a3617db6ffd7d9c9","after_hash":"5efa19b58ec62988d15dc797a949e32fb32f30e90e0a9933f64966752477dc8d"}
